column1: # Title: Mapping file of FAO primary Ag products to commodities in GCAM and other database
# Description: Maps FAO PRODSTAT crops to GCAM commodities and crop names in all other databases.
# item and item_code are both updated for primary (land-based) crops  (Pumpkins for Fodder has data issue so not mapped).
# FAO only has price data for items with TRUE for price_item.
